result.reason: 7-year-old issue (2018) with no user response since 2019; autologin failure on single Windows 7 Pro machine while others work indicates CredSSP/NLA configuration issue (see #875), not a code bug — Windows 7 is EOL and modern error handling already added in f0d7ca5da
result.approach: No code fix needed — environment/configuration issue. User should enable UseCredSsp on the connection. Reference #875 for CredSSP guidance.
